{"title":"三条扁担——越南诗抄","authors":["孙滨"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三条扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——越南诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个参加修路的姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都挑着一样的箩筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像三个姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来来往往都在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘飘荡荡的头巾下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三张玫瑰色的脸儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三条扁担在肩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪呀闪地闪成一个点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁路在进行整修，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人们一个接着一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把石料和泥土向工地运送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们也来参加。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗡！火车过来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个姑娘也都站下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登时掀起一片欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们的声音最响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联老大哥！你好！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国同志们！你好！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车里也送来欢呼和鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的车站沸腾了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这满载着友谊的火车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给姑娘们带来无限的鼓舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那三条扁担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪呀闪地闪成一个点……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}